title: Shark FX v9.0.4.1162 x64 [deepstatus]
description:
Shark FX v9.0.4.1162 x64 [deepstatus]





Introducing, new Shark FX version 9, a powerful new way of designing
Experience a new world of 3D design capabilities for printing, rendering,
animation and precise manufacturing. Shark FX V9 has the ability to
retain the control mesh as part of a feature tree for rapid design
iterations that involve mesh and precise feature operations. State of the
art technology converts meshes into optimized smooth NURB models suitable
for solid modeling operations, including blending, chamfering and
shelling, plus exporting to .dwg, IGES and STEP file formats. The all-new
Shark FX v9 - Your complete design solution - Unmatched Versatility -
Unbeatable Value - Unprecedented Precision


Also included:

PowerPack Pro
The Pro configuration includes all the features in standard plus:
Conversion from general mesh to analytic solids
Convert from quad meshes to NURBs surface or solids
Precise coordinate comparison between mesh and NURBS
Alignment tools between mesh and NURBs
Profile repair and validate

- Unrar with you favorite archiver, such as WinRar

- Install.

- Do not launch Shark FX yet..

- Copy crack to installation dir
